<html lang='en'>
	<head>
		<meta charset='UTF-8' />
		<meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
		<title>Invoice</title>
		<style>

			*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; } body { font-family:
			Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #fff; } .page
			{ break-after: page; } .invoice { padding: 0 2rem 2rem; } .invoice-header
			{ display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
			.invoice-header-left { width: 32%; } .invoice-code { display: flex;
			justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; } .invoice-body-1 {
			display: grid; gap: 2px; background-color: #000; padding: 2px;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } .invoice-body { background-color: #fff;
			padding: 20px; } .item1 { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 1 / span 2; } .item4{
			grid-column: 1 / span 2; grid-row: 3; text-align: center; } .item4 > p {
			text-align: justify; } .item8 {grid-column: 1 / span 2; } .buyer-details {
			display:flex; flex-direction:column; width:33%; } .invoice-table { width:
			100%; border-collapse: collapse; } .invoice-table th, .invoice-table td {
			border: 1px solid #000; padding: 8px; text-align: center; } .invoice-table
			th { background-color: #f2f2f2; } .invoice-total { margin-top: 20px; }
			.invoice-footer { margin-top: 20px; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class='page'>
			<div class='invoice'>
				<div class='invoice-header'>
					<div class='invoice-header-left'>
						<h3>{{buyer.name}}</h3>
						<div>{{buyer.address.address_line1}}</div>
						<div>{{buyer.address.address_line2}}</div>
						<div>{{buyer.address.city}}
							-
							{{buyer.address.pincode}}
							{{buyer.address.state}}
							{{buyer.address.country}}
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class='invoice-header-right'>
						<img
							height='100px'
							width='100px'
							src='https://logodix.com/logo/974856.jpg'
							alt='Reliance Retail Limited'
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class='invoice-code'>
					<h2>SELLER</h2>
					<h2>PURCHASE ORDER</h2>
					<img
						width='184'
						height='24'
						src='data:image/jpg;base64,'
					/>
				</div>
				<div class='invoice-body-1'>
					<div class='invoice-body item1'>
						<p>
							<div>Vendor Code : {{supplier_details.code}}</div>
							<div>{{supplier_details.name}}</div>
						</p>

						<div>{{supplier_details.address.address_line1}}</div>
						<div>{{supplier_details.address.address_line2}}</div>
						<div>
							{{supplier_details.address.city}}
							{{supplier_details.address.state}}
						</div>
						<div>
							Pincode :
							{{supplier_details.address.pincode}},
							{{supplier_details.address.country}}
						</div>

						<div>Email: {{supplier_details.contact.email}}</div>
						<div>Pan No: {{supplier_details.pan}}</div>
						<div>Vendor Status: 01 - {{supplier_details.supplier_status}}</div>
						<div>GSTIN No: {{supplier_details.gst_no}}</div>
						<div>Attention : </div>
					</div>
					<div class='invoice-body item2'>
						<div>PO NO : {{po_number}} Site: {{site_details.code}}</div>
						<div>PO Date: {{po_date}}</div>
					</div>
					<div class='invoice-body item3'>
					</div>
					<div class='invoice-body item4'>
						<h2>{{site_details.name}}</h2>
						<p>
							In accepting this PURCHASE ORDER, SELLER agrees to furnish the
							GOODS specified in full accordance with all conditions set forth
							herein and / or attachments hereto. All drawings, designs,
							specifications and other data prepared by OWNER and related
							thereto arethe property of the OWNER and must be returned to OWNER
							upon completionby SELLER of the obligations under this PURCHASE
							ORDER. Theinformation contained herein is not to be released or
							disclosed for any other use or purpose other than for the
							execution of this PURCHASE ORDER. This formal PURCHASE ORDER
							constitutes the entire agreement and only written changes by way
							of an amendment to this PURCHASE ORDER will be legally binding. It
							is important that SELLER signs and returns the PURCHASE ORDER copy
							within three (3) days of receipt. No other form of acceptance will
							be accepted. Failure to return the acceptance does not diminish
							the responsibilities as set forth herein, but may result in a
							delay to any payments that may be due and may be cause for
							termination of this PURCHASE ORDER.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class='invoice-body item5'>
						<div>Delivery Address : </div>
						<div>
							{{site_details.address.address_line1}}
						</div>
						<div>
							{{site_details.address.address_line2}}
						</div>
						<div>{{site_details.address.state}},
							{{site_details.address.city}}
							-
							{{site_details.address.pincode}}</div>
						<div>Tel: {{supplier_details.contact.phone}}</div>
						<div>GSTN No: {{supplier_details.gst_no}}</div>
						<div>Email No: {{supplier_details.contact.email}}</div>
					</div>
					<div class='invoice-body item2'>
						<p style='display: flex; justify-content: space-between;'>
							<span
								style='
						width: 125pt;'
							>BASIC VALUE</span>
							<span style='align-self: center;'>INR</span>
							<span
								style='
						width: 75pt;'
							>{{total_base_value}}</span>
						</p>
						<p style='display: flex; justify-content: space-between;'>
							<span
								style='
						width: 125pt;'
							>TOTAL IGST</span>
							<span style='align-self: center;'>INR</span>
							<span
								style='
						width: 75pt;'
							>{{gst.total_igst_value}}</span>
						</p>
					</div>

					<div
						style='grid-column: 1 / span 2;
			text-align: center;'
					>
						<div style='background-color: #fff; display: flex'>
							<div style='width:48%' class='invoice-body item6'>
							</div>
							<div style='width:52%' class='invoice-body item7'>
								<p style='display: flex; justify-content: space-between;'>
									<span
										style='
						width: 125pt;'
									>Total Order Value :</span>
									<span style='align-self: center;'>INR</span>
									<span
										style='
						width: 75pt;'
									>{{total_order_value}}</span>
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class='invoice-body'>
						<p>DELIVERY DATE : {{delivery_date}} </p>
						<p>Payment Terms : See Page Inside</p>
					</div>
					<div class='invoice-body'>
						<p>DELIVERY TERM : {{delivery_terms}} </p>
					</div>

					<div class='invoice-body item8'>
					</div>

					<div
						style='grid-column: 1 / span 2;
			text-align: center;'
					>
						<div style='display: flex; column-gap: 2px;'>
							<div
								style='text-align: left;'
								class='invoice-body item9 buyer-details'
							>
								<p>Buyer : {{buyer.name}} </p>
								<p>Phone : {{buyer.contact.phone}} </p>
								<p>Email : {{buyer.contact.email}} </p>
							</div>
							<div
								style='justify-content: space-between'
								class='invoice-body item10 buyer-details'
							>
								<div>
									<p>For {{site_details.name}}</p>
									<p>{{buyer.name}} </p>

								</div>
								<p>
									This is computer generated document not requiring any
									signature
								</p>
							</div>
							<div
								style='justify-content: space-between'
								class='invoice-body item11 buyer-details'
							>
								<p>SELLER&#39;S Acceptence</p>
								<p
									style='display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top:25px'
								>
									<span>Signautre</span>
									<span>Title</span>
									<span>Date</span>
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
				<div class='invoice-footer'>
					<p>Registered Office : {{buyer.registered_address}}</p>
					<p>CIN No. </p>
					<p>Please connect with &#39;rr.vigilance@ril.com&#39; or Toll-free
						number: 18008903477 to report any unethical incident violating any
						terms &amp; conditions.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class='page'>
			<div class='invoice'>
				<div class='invoice-body'>
					<table class='invoice-table'>
						<thead>
							<tr>
								<th>SR. NO.</th>
								<th>Article No. <br /> HSN Code</th>
								<th>EAN No. <br /> Vendor Article No <br /> Vendor Item No</th>
								<th>Material Description<br /> Delivery Date <br />Site</th>
								<th>Quantity</th>
								<th>UOM</th>
								<th>MRP</th>
								<th>Base Cost</th>
								<th>IGST (%)<br /> CESS (%)</th>
								<th>IGST <br /> CESS </th>
								<th>Total Base Value</th>
							</tr>
						</thead>
						<tbody>
							{{#each po_item}}
								{{#each this.items}}
									<tr>
										<td>{{inc @index}}</td>
										<td>{{this.article_no}}<br />{{this.hsn_code}}</td>
										<td>{{this.ean_no}}<br />{{this.vendor_article_no}}<br
											/>{{this.vendor_item_no}}</td>
										<td>{{this.material_description}}<br />{{delivery_date}}<br
											/>{{site_details.name}}</td>
										<td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
										<td>{{this.uom}}</td>
										<td>{{this.mrp}}</td>
										<td>{{this.base_cost}}</td>
										<td>{{this.igst}}<br />{{this.cess}}</td>
										<td>{{this.igst_amount}}<br />{{this.cess_amount}}</td>
										<td>{{this.total_base_value}}</td>
									</tr>
								{{/each}}
								<tr>
									<td colspan='4'>Sub Total of Qty</td>
									<td>{{this.total_quantity}}</td>
									<td></td>
									<td></td>
									<td></td>
									<td></td>
									<td></td>
									<td></td>
								</tr>
							{{/each}}
							<tr>
								<td colspan='4'>Grand Total of Qty</td>
								<td>{{grand_total_quantity}}</td>
								<td></td>
								<td></td>
								<td></td>
								<td></td>
								<td></td>
								<td></td>
							</tr>
							<tr>
								<td colspan='4'></td>
								<td colspan='5'>TOTAL BASIC VALUE</td>
								<td>INR</td>
								<td>{{total_base_value}}</td>
							</tr>
							<tr>
								<td colspan='4'></td>
								<td colspan='5'>TOTAL IGST</td>
								<td>INR</td>
								<td>{{gst.total_igst_value}}</td>
							</tr>
							<tr>
								<td colspan='4'></td>
								<td colspan='5'>TOTAL Order Value: </td>
								<td>INR</td>
								<td>{{total_order_value}}</td>
							</tr>
						</tbody>
					</table>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class='page'>
			<div class='invoice'>
				<div class='invoice-static-body'>
					<h3
						style='
				padding-top: 4pt;
				padding-left: 14pt;
				text-indent: 0pt;
				text-align: left;
			'
					>
						Terms of payment :
					</h3>
					<p
						style='
				padding-top: 1pt;
				padding-left: 14pt;
				text-indent: 0pt;
				text-align: left;
			'
					>
						Pro-rata payment(s) shall be made within 30 days from the date of
						receipt of GOODS, or receipt of correct invoice &amp; dispatch
						documents whichever is later.
					</p>
					<p style='text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left'><br /></p>
					<h4 style='padding-left: 14pt; text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left'>
						Note(S) :
					</h4>
					<p
						style='
				padding-top: 4pt;
				padding-left: 14pt;
				text-indent: 0pt;
				line-height: 115%;
				text-align: justify;
			'
					>
						» It is essential that the seller shall mention Item No &amp; Item
						code along with corresponding Material Description and P.O. No. as
						mentioned above, in the Delivery challan(On-Shore Order) / Packing
						List (Off-shore Order) and invoice for ease of material Inwarding
						and Bill Processing.It is also essential that the Seller attaches a
						Tag /Sticker with each item indicating item Code &amp; PO No.
						Failure to do so may be the grounds for the rejection(s) or delay in
						release of payment(s).
					</p>
					<p style='text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left'><br /></p>
					<h4 style='padding-left: 14pt; text-indent: 0pt; text-align: justify'>
						»
						<span class='p'>Suppliers need to call the destination DC/Store
							atleast 24 hrs in advance to schedule the delivery time for
							goods.Vehicles without prior appointment could be subject to
							delay.</span>
					</h4>
					<p style='text-indent: 0pt; text-align: left'><br /></p>
					<h3 style='padding-left: 14pt; text-indent: 0pt; text-align: justify'>
						GSTIN Number Details:
					</h3>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>